export const API_LOGIN = `${DOMAIN}login`

export const API_REGISTER_CUSTOMER = `${DOMAIN}register/customer`

export const API_ACCOMMODATION = `${DOMAIN}create/accommodation`
export const API_ENTERTAINMENT = `${DOMAIN}create/entertainment`
export const API_RESTAURANT = `${DOMAIN}create/restaurant`
export const API_GET_ALL_SERVICE = `${DOMAIN}service`
export const API_GET_SERVICE_BY_CONDITION = `${DOMAIN}service`
export const API_PUT_UPDATE_SERVICEACCOMMODATION = `${DOMAIN}update/accommodation/`

export const API_SERVICE_CONFIRM = `${DOMAIN}approve/service`
export const API_PUT_UPDATE_SERVICEENTERTAIMENT = `${DOMAIN}update/entertainment/`
export const API_PUT_UPDATE_SERVICERESTAURANT = `${DOMAIN}update/restaurant/`
export const API_POST_CREATE_TOUR = `${DOMAIN}create/tour`

export const API_DELETE_TOUR = `${DOMAIN}delete/tour`
